[I] Fast library for manipulating YAML

[T] Rapid YAML or ryml, is a library to parse and emit YAML, and do it fast.
[T] Ryml has respect for your build times and therefore is NOT header-only.
[T] It has no dependencies, not even on the STL (although it does use the
[T] libc).

[U] https://github.com/biojppm/rapidyaml/

